I"y<p>A ginger biscuit, ginger nut or ginger snap is a globally popular biscuit based snack food, flavoured with ginger.</p>

<p>Ginger biscuits are flavoured with powdered ginger and a variety of other spices, most commonly cinnamon, molasses and nutmeg. There are many recipes for ginger nuts.</p>

